#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/resteasy-reactive.adoc:1365
msgid "Then we can define how to read and write it with our body reader/writers, annotated with link:{jaxrsapi}/javax/ws/rs/ext/Provider.html[`@Provider`]:"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/resteasy-reactive.adoc:1376
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/resteasy-reactive.adoc:1440
